node_2.subject: Isabella Rodriguez
node_2.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, open Hobbs Cafe at 8:00 am, work at the counter and interact with customers until 3:00 pm, take a break and have lunch at 12:00 pm, prepare for the Valentine's Day party at 3:30 pm, welcome customers and prepare food and drinks for the party from 5:00 pm to 7:00 pm, clean up and close the cafe at 8:00 pm.
